USAGE

For module usage instructions, please see the POD documentation in the
file.

 $ perldoc lib/Text/TEI/Markup.pm


PREREQUISITES

Text::TEI::Markup requires:

* perl >= 5.8.3
* XML::LibXML


INSTALL

From the command shell, run:

 $ perl -MCPAN -e "install Text::TEI::Markup"

or uncompress the package and run the standard sequence:

 $ perl Makefile.PL && make && make test && make install


